OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGlobal supply chain: Lego  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto build $1bn factory in   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FVietnam                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Lego has announced plans to build a new
OL,6, manufacturing operation in Vietnam to  
OL,7, keep up with growing demand for its    
OL,8, products in Asia.                      
OL,10,FThe toymaking giant said it will invest
OL,11,Fmore than $1bn (#760m) in the project, 
OL,12,Fwhich will be near the country's main  
OL,13,Fbusiness hub of Ho Chi Minh City.      
OL,15,FIt will be the Danish company's second 
OL,16,Ffactory in Asia after it opened a plant
OL,17,Fin China five years ago.               
OL,19,FThe firm has seen double-digit growth  
OL,20,Fin the region since 2019.              
